text: Lag raha jaise hogayi life apni set
Pehle kar lunga mai CA uske baad dedunga CAT
Local college me awai leliya, B.Com me admission
CA Exam par kar lunga focus, side me graduation
yaha har kahani ki happy ending nahi hoti
4 saal lagaye maine, Na CA hua na CAT.
Mummy boli shadi karle papa ki shop jaake baith
Bas B.Com ki degree thi and that too from local college
Na Job mili na respect mili
MLM ke chakkar me dosto ne naata toda,
Insurance ke naam pe kharid liya tha ULIP,
No money left to buy stocks at the dip
iss baar laga khud ki bhi sun le
Youtube se seekh seekh kar main
Video Editing, Content Writing aur even di fitness training
Aise hi ek session me hui Rishabh se mulakaat
Bina money ko mind kare ki LLA ki shuruaat
Apni galtiyon se jo seekha hai bas wahi tumhe bataya
